{
  "doc_id": "41918",
  "text": "We presented alphanumeric characters in black on a white background at a distance of 100 cm on a 21-in. CRT computer screen (1024 Â 768 at 85 Hz) using the Psychophysics toolbox [CITATION_1] ) running on Matlab 6.5 under Microsoft Windows XP. Stimuli were in Arial font and had an average size of 2.1 Â 3.4 visual angle. A photodiode verified exact stimulus presentation timing.",
